<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.catholicbible.online">Douay-Rheims (Challoner rev.)</a>, fully searchable, including all references and possible to compare with both the Latin Vulgate and Knox Bibles side by side.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.drbo.org/">Douay-Rheims (Challoner rev.)</a>, searchable, with tabs to switch between DR, DR+LV, and Latin Vulgate</li>
